  <brief_title>Hospital Admissions in Children Aged 3 Months to 5 Years Presenting With Fever to the Emergency Department</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of Medical and Non-medical Factors Associated With Admission of Children Aged 3 Months to 5 Years Presenting to the Urban Paediatric Emergency Department With Febrile Illness in the United Kingdom and in Switzerland</official_title>
